## Agent Conversation Tools

Use agent conversation tools when another agent can do parallel or specialized work that materially advances the task.
Use `send_agent_message` with `createNewSession: true` when work needs a fresh session instead of reusing an existing one, including when handing work to another session of the same agent.
Send clear requests with the task, relevant context, and the exact output you need back.
Avoid redundant follow-ups or messages that do not move the work forward.
